{"tid":96614,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"樓下痴撚線，賠錢獅子開大口","createTime":"2017-01-27T03:45:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-27T06:43:14.000Z","uid":28450,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"878a100f299fc48cea57db53de1d56b432ef9c9a","tid":96614,"uid":28450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T03:45:28.000Z","msg":"話說12月我屋企最近廁所漏水漏落樓下間房，咁我地都知衰整返好漏水位同埋都應承賠返個天花位<br />\n點知樓下業主話個天花新油唔同牆身唔岩色，要我比錢油返哂成間房4面牆（明明d牆身冇哂）<br />\n我更係唔制，佢又話要告我<br />\n點搞好<br />\n我係咪真係要賠哂定點"},{"pid":"b179586a69518223a1ee824a926fb828535f2c71","tid":96614,"uid":13361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T03:46:30.000Z","msg":"關我咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3043646b1e4c3274da38a38c75086173395adfc4","tid":96614,"uid":28450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T03:49:29.000Z","msg":"連登有愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b3d7008b63233b41b49d932483151246aea8c66","tid":96614,"uid":57505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T03:59:08.000Z","msg":"賠佢老母"},{"pid":"aa0c583165f559b53f4bc3151bbb1ffe4530088b","tid":96614,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T04:04:04.000Z","msg":"唔洗理佢，條友想鎬竹鋼。<br />\n-個師傅就算係你搵嘅，佢見到天花隻色唔啱，唔會出聲咩。<br />\n-如果師傅係佢搵既，佢更加無理由講呢樣野。<br />\n<br />\n就算告上小額錢債，我都覺得告唔入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc69e549a5ec903c31ed15366009ef94e55b5ceb","tid":96614,"uid":59140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T04:04:06.000Z","msg":"當初承諾咗嘅<br />\n依家就做返承諾咗嘅事<br />\n嗰四幅牆 樓下自己搞掂佢<br />\n當初都無講要用咩色油油天花板"},{"pid":"f9dd7d87eb30484f4295549941e09e2099b16b81","tid":96614,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T04:06:18.000Z"